q_ch: William 的缝纫任务进度如何？
q_en: What is the progress of sewing tasks for William?

command: SELECT id FROM customers WHERE customer_name = 'William';
SELECT id FROM orders WHERE user_id = 'c8';
SELECT id FROM order_product WHERE order_id IN (SELECT id FROM orders WHERE user_id = 'c8');

SELECT SUM(planned_number) AS total_planned_sewing, SUM(completed_number) AS total_completed_sewing FROM sewing_tasks WHERE order_product_id IN (SELECT id FROM order_product WHERE order_id IN (SELECT id FROM orders WHERE user_id = 'c8'));

SELECT (total_completed_sewing / total_planned_sewing) * 100 AS sewing_progress FROM (SELECT SUM(planned_number) AS total_planned_sewing, SUM(completed_number) AS total_completed_sewing FROM sewing_tasks WHERE order_product_id IN (SELECT id FROM order_product WHERE order_id IN (SELECT id FROM orders WHERE user_id = 'c8'))) AS sewing;
